<ab facs="#facs_120_r2l13">Burger / vvie daʒ Jm <expan>Albr<ex>echt</ex></expan> Seÿler hinter euch geſeſʒen ſein habe </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_120_line_1592305382036_49">cʒu <expan>ham<ex>m</ex>erſtoꝛff</expan> / 
<del rend="strikethrough">mit dem rechten </del> bekümert habe / 
<add><ab facs="#facs_120_r1l1">vnd vvir doch <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nomen</expan> </ab><ab facs="#facs_120_r1l2"><expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> daʒ khein gebant </ab><ab facs="#facs_120_r1l3">gericht da nıht ſeÿ / </ab></add>
<add><ab facs="#facs_120_r2l14">
<del rend="strikethrough">vnd doch kein gebant <expan>ger<ex>iht</ex></expan>
